	eet add-on tickets are sold separately. To attend the M&G\, fans must also
	 purchase a ticket to the event. Show starts at 8pm. There will be a 20-mi
	nute intermission. Ages 18+ welcome w/ Valid ID for entry. Check DragFans.
	com and HereIsBosco.com for tour info VIP Tables seat 4 humans and are fir
	st come first serve if you purchase in that section. Please arrive early s
	o that our hosts may seat your party together.\nMurray & Peter Present: "T
